[[File:Orbitalstrikerifle.jpg|thumb|The Orbital Strike]]
The '''Orbital Strike''' was a single-shot [[Sniper rifle/Legends|sniper rifle]] that fired a [[Flare stick|beacon]] at a remote target. After five seconds, a [[Turbolaser/Legends|Turbolaser]], or a [[Ion cannon/Legends|ion cannon]] beam fired from a ship that was in orbit above at the beacon, causing huge destruction. However if someone was able to destroy the beacon in the five seconds, the strike would be averted.

